        {
            "title": "財經｜同仁堂醫養(02667)招股籌近9億 入場費4192元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜同仁堂醫養(02667)招股籌近9億 入場費4192元\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜同仁堂醫養(02667)招股籌近9億 入場費4192元</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">同仁堂旗下中醫醫療服務集團同仁堂醫養(02667)今天起至下周三(3月25日)招股，發售1.08億股H股，香港公開發售佔10%，國際配售佔90%。每股招股價介乎7.3元至8.3元，集資最多8.98億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一手500股，入場費4191.85元。股份預計3月30日上市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司擬將所得款項淨額中，47.5%擴充中醫醫療服務網絡、23.6%提升中醫醫療服務能力、18.9%償還若干未償還銀行貸款，餘下10%作營運資金及其他一般企業用途。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E5%90%8C%E4%BB%81%E5%A0%82%E9%86%AB%E9%A4%8A-02667-%E6%8B%9B%E8%82%A1%E7%B1%8C%E8%BF%919%E5%84%84-%E5%85%A5%E5%A0%B4%E8%B2%BB4192%E5%85%83-004014158.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 08:56:07",
